= Hydra TODO

== Rsync
Split SSH into:

  connect: user@site.com
  ssh_options: -p 3022

Then make an rsync section:

  rsync:
    source: /path/to/code/locally
    exclude:
      - tmp
      - log
      - config/test/database.yml
      - db/*.sqlite3
      etc...

options: -az

== Setup

Provide a hydra:setup task to override to be run remotely before testing





